rows.label: qst106013_0010
rows.name: Internal pressure remain stable.

rows.label: qst106013_0020
rows.name: Dadapon, crank up voltage a bit further!

rows.label: qst106013_0030
rows.name: Tora! Increasing load even more maybe dangerous!

rows.label: qst106013_0040
rows.name: Levels not there yet, Dadapon!

rows.label: qst106013_0050
rows.name: We not cross the line...but we step on it!

rows.label: qst106013_0060
rows.name:
OK!
Kiku! Look closely at meter doodah!

rows.label: qst106013_0070
rows.name: Yes, Masterpon!

rows.label: qst106013_0080
rows.name: Hoo-hoo! Preparations are prepared.

rows.label: qst106013_0090
rows.name: Kiku! Hit switch!

rows.label: qst106013_0100
rows.name: Roger, Masterpon!

rows.label: qst106013_0110
rows.name:
OK, Hana!
Wakey wakey!

rows.label: qst106013_0120
rows.name:
Hey, what's this?!
Leaving us in the dark?

rows.label: qst106013_0130
rows.name: I... I can't see a thing!

rows.label: qst106013_0140
rows.name: What... Did something go wrong?

rows.label: qst106013_0150
rows.name: I don't know...

rows.label: qst106013_0160
rows.name:
The lights went out the first time
we started Hana up too, remember?

rows.label: qst106013_0170
rows.name: Isn't it...taking a bit long, though...?

rows.label: qst106013_0180
rows.name: Ah...yeah...

rows.label: qst106013_0190
rows.name: Whoaa!

rows.label: qst106013_0200
rows.name: Wh-what is it...?

rows.label: qst106013_0210
rows.name:
*hack* *splutter*
Was that a lightning bolt or something?

rows.label: qst106013_0220
rows.name: Everyone OK?

rows.label: qst106013_0230
rows.name:
I'm OK.
But what about Hana?! How's she doing?!

rows.label: qst106013_0240
rows.name:
Woohoo! Success!
Look! Glorious birth of Hana JD!

rows.label: qst106013_0250
rows.name: ...urgh...uh...

rows.label: qst106013_0260
rows.name:
Ah!
Good morning, everybody!

rows.label: qst106013_0270
rows.name:
Uh? Huh?
M-morning...?

rows.label: qst106013_0280
rows.name: So...this is the new Hana-chan?

rows.label: qst106013_0290
rows.name:
Cool! I'm starting to think there's something
in Tora's science malarkey after all!

rows.label: qst106013_0300
rows.name:
Hana's an adult now?
Talk about a growth spurt...

rows.label: qst106013_0310
rows.name: What's up, Nia? Jealous much?

rows.label: qst106013_0320
rows.name:
Shut it, Zeke! Unless you want me to
remodel your face!

rows.label: qst106013_0330
rows.name:
Come, Hana!
Give us demonstration of new power!

rows.label: qst106013_0340
rows.name: Roger roger, Masterpon!

rows.label: qst106013_0350
rows.name:
W-whoa, Hana!
Masterpon has own legs!

rows.label: qst106013_0360
rows.name: Masterpon have very short legs.

rows.label: qst106013_0370
rows.name:
Much more efficient like this when
Masterpon travel with Hana.

rows.label: qst106013_0380
rows.name:
This very silly.
And big disrespect to your Masterpon!

rows.label: qst106013_0390
rows.name:
Hahaha! You look like Hana's
little teddy bear there, Tora.

rows.label: qst106013_0400
rows.name: Meh-meh...!

rows.label: qst106013_0410
rows.name: Tora is not little teddy bear!

rows.label: qst106013_0420
rows.name:
Put Tora down, Hana!
Right now!

rows.label: qst106013_0430
rows.name:
Hey, it's not so bad.
At least you don't have to walk.

rows.label: qst106013_0440
rows.name: Tora does not like.

rows.label: qst106013_0450
rows.name:
Tora is grown-up big adult...
Hana, come on! Hana!!!
